                        "name": "bittarman",
                        "displayName": "Ryan Mauger",
                        "active": true
                    },
                    "body": "This is not a problem of Zend_Form, rather that you are using magic quotes, which it is commonly agreed, should *not* be relied upon.\n\nYou should turn of magic quotes.",
